{
  "id": "adv_event_2307_01_01",
  "title": "含みのある\n言葉",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "テレビ番組の、生放送の仕事……ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A live TV show… you say?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.2460318565,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "はい。毎週ゲストに芸能人を呼んで、MCのアイドルと\nいろんなゲームで対決する……という番組ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. It's a show where celebrities compete\nin various games with idol host.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.4333333333,
      "endTime": 13.7797963461,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "夏の特番生放送にスリクスのみなさんに\n出てもらいたいとのことです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They want all of you from ⅢX to be guests\non the summer special live broadcast.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.9767352422,
      "endTime": 18.505896028000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "ふふん。特番のゲストなら、まあまあかな\nたまには{user}も仕事するもんだね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Heh‚ being a guest on a special isn't too bad.\nLooks like {user}-san is finally doing some work for a change.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.7028349241,
      "endTime": 26.7058960279,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "はは……たまには、ですか……\nそれで、撮影では海辺に特設セットを組むみたいで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha… only for a change‚ huh?\nSo‚ it looks like they'll set up a special set on the beach for the filming.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.9028349241,
      "endTime": 34.9030164083,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "……海？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…The beach?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.0999553045,
      "endTime": 36.3593596537,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "海、ですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The beach?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.5666158676,
      "endTime": 38.2808577776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "ってことは、海に行けるんですか？\n当然、旅費はそちら持ちですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ we get to go to the beach?\nAnd the travel costs are covered‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.4666173935,
      "endTime": 44.6832839012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです\n分かってるとは思いますけど、仕事ですからね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course.\nBut remember‚ it's still a job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.8802227974,
      "endTime": 49.5680912018,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "分かってますって\nでも、海に行くのも久しぶりなので、つい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Got it.\nBut‚ it's been a while since I've been to the beach‚ so I'm excited.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.765030098,
      "endTime": 55.6843271256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくだし、水着買っちゃおうかな～\n海行くなら、写真撮り溜めておかなきゃ意味ないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I might as well buy a new swimsuit then.\nIf we're going to the beach‚ we have to take lots of pictures.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.8812660218,
      "endTime": 62.5890209199,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "……海に着ていけるような水着\nどこかにあったかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I wonder if I have a swimsuit\nsuitable for the beach.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.7812660218,
      "endTime": 66.3120144368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん、海に行くことしか考えてませんけど\nまずは番組の撮影、よろしくお願いしますね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ you're only thinking about going to the beach.\nPlease remember‚ the main thing is to shoot the show…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.5145993551,
      "endTime": 73.6463454566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ？　さっきからうるさいなー\n仕事ってことくらいちゃんと分かってますけどー？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? You're so annoying.\nWe know it's work‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.8432843527,
      "endTime": 79.92931607579999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、そう言えば\n番組のMCのアイドルっていうのは誰なんです？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ by the way‚\nwho’s the idol host for the show?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.1432843527,
      "endTime": 85.6042140326,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "『恋々Poison』。デビューは私達より後だけど\n今のランクは確か、私達や月ストよりも上のはず",
      "translations": {
        "en": "'Lovesick Poison'. They debuted after us‚\nbut their rank is higher than ours and Moon Tempest's.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.8011529288,
      "endTime": 94.1297240576,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "スタッフやテレビ局の評判もいいそうだし\n今、一番勢いのあるグループの一つでしょうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They have a good reputation among staff and TV networks‚\nand they're one of the most popular groups right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.3344862622,
      "endTime": 100.88952023210001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……俺より詳しい解説、ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thank you for the detailed explanation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.1011529288,
      "endTime": 104.6511529288,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "他のアイドルの賑やかしなのは気に食わないですけど\nま、テレビに出られるのは悪い話じゃないですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t like being overshadowed by other idols‚\nbut being on TV isn't a bad thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.848091825,
      "endTime": 113.20178750369999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。ライブバトルなら全力で勝ちにいきますけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "True. If it were a live battle‚ we’d go all out to win.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.3987263999,
      "endTime": 117.8673202834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "今回はバラエティだもんね\n撮れ高稼いで、目立てば上出来っしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But this is a variety show.\nIf we get good airtime and stand out‚ that’s a win.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.0653930666,
      "endTime": 123.6987265589,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました。では、近々打ち合わせが入ると思うので\nその時はよろしくお願いしますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understood. There will be a meeting soon‚\nso please be prepared for that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.8987263999,
      "endTime": 129.89103911729998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後、打ち合わせ当日。テレビ局",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later‚ the day of the meeting. TV network",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.7666666667,
      "endTime": 132.36666666669998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.5046446802
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "前は確か、この辺に自販機があったと思うんだけど……\nしばらく来ない間に、撤去されたかな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought there was a vending machine around here before…\nDid they remove it while I was away?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.3879739445,
      "endTime": 143.7040738743,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob2",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01-hanano001.m4a",
      "text": "こんにちは！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.8879739445,
      "endTime": 145.2279709261,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.421304226
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　間違ってたら悪いんだけど、もしかして\n『恋々Poison』の、華乃ちゃん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? If I'm not mistaken‚\naren't you Kano-chan from 'Lovesick Poison'?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.421304226,
      "endTime": 152.79733591090002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob2",
      "speakerName": "華乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hanano",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01-hanano002.m4a",
      "text": "そうです、華乃です！\nkanaちゃんに覚えてもらってたなんて、嬉しい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I'm Kano!\nI'm so happy you remember me‚ kana-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.9716701825,
      "endTime": 158.21462761569998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 158.4212940534
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_01-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん知ってるよ～！\nテレビでも動画サイトでも、見ない日ないもん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course I know you~!\nI see you on TV and video sites every day!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.4212940534,
      "endTime": 164.4032670339,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 164.5879607201
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob2",
      "speakerName": "華乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hanano",
